videos.headline: Purdue QB picked off on opening drive
videos.description: Michigan State opens the game with an interception, as Purdue QB David Blough rolls right and throws an errant pass that is picked off by David Dowell.

videos.headline: Michigan State QB with mean stiff-arm
videos.description: Michigan State QB Rocky Lombardi keeps on the triple-option read and gets planted on a 6-yard gain, but not before he unleashes a mean stiff-arm on a Purdue defender.

videos.headline: Lombardi money on first career TD pass
videos.description: Michigan State QB Rocky Lombardi hits Darrell Stewart Jr. on an 11-yard back-shoulder touchdown throw, the first of his college career.

videos.headline: Purdue's big strike sets up TD run
videos.description: Purdue QB David Blough connects with Brycen Hopkins on a 30-yard gain, setting up a 1-yard touchdown for Terry Wright.

videos.headline: Michigan State LB lays monstrous hit, steals INT
videos.description: Brycen Hopkins makes a catch, but he is pounded by Tyriq Thompson, who jars the ball loose and snags it for a Michigan State interception.

videos.headline: Michigan State puts game on ice with big INT
videos.description: Michigan State's Matt Morrissey breaks on a David Blough pass for the game-sealing interception to give the Spartans a 23-13 win vs. Purdue.
